<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦跳进水里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用力拉了拉王子的肩膀，但是没有用。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她浮出水面换了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怎么办？水已经涨到王子的眼睛了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦把王子的头往后仰，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样他的鼻子和嘴就能露出水面了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！他没有呼吸了！”艾伦非常惊慌，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我该怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，“爱”和“水”给了艾伦巨大的勇气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她再一次潜入水中，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>用所有的力气抓着王子往上拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，王子的一只手臂从洞里出来了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的身体也很快跟着出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>朋友们，没有人知道公主是怎么把王子弄上船的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但不管怎么样，公主做到了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她用最快的速度把船划到岸边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她再次用全身的力气，把王子拖到了岸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子脸色苍白，双眼紧紧地闭着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太迟了。”艾伦心想，“他死了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦的心很痛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的身体发出了奇怪的声音，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>眼中充满了……泪水！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人生第一次，艾伦哭了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123347</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她哭的时候，天空也开始下雨了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过这不是普通的雨，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而是像红宝石、蓝宝石、绿宝石那样彩色的雨！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雨越下越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，金色的水从山上流了下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>河流又开始流动起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>婴儿的眼里也有了小小的泪花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>湖水越涨越高。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同时，艾格尼丝地下室里的水也越涨越高！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咣！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汹涌的湖水冲破了地下室的门，涌上台阶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！不！”艾格尼丝尖叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>强大的水流带走了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦一直在哭，她哭得很伤心，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有看到王子睁开了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在为我哭泣吗？”王子问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还活着！”公主兴奋地跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是她没有飘走，反而摔在了地上！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你摔在地上了！”王子很惊讶，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也就是说……你有重量了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王国里的每个人都非常开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，艾伦和王子就结婚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们生了很多孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当然！每个孩子都有重量。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从此，他们幸福地生活在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>